videos.description: The corner 3-pointer from Jaylen Barford bounces off the rim to the top of the backboard and back into the net.
videos.headline: Arkansas' 3-pointer bounces off top of board into basket

videos.description: Off the fast break, Egor Koulechov passes over to Mike Okauru in the corner who makes the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Florida with another catch-and-shoot 3-pointer

videos.description: Daniel Gafford waits in the paint then grabs the offensive board and throws down the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Gafford slams putback dunk

videos.description: Adrio Bailey gets the tough layup to go in the paint giving the Razorbacks their first lead of the game just before halftime.
videos.headline: Contested layup gives Arkansas the lead

videos.description: Jaylen Barford drives through the paint then scores a layup over the Florida defender.
videos.headline: Barford makes acrobatic layup for Arkansas

videos.description: Jaylen Barford drives through the crowded paint and banks in the layup near the top of the backboard.
videos.headline: Barford banks in shot high off the glass

videos.description: Jaylen Barford knocks down the 3-pointer near the wing that sends the Arkansas bench and fans on their feet.
videos.headline: 3-pointer from Barford gets Arkansas fans excited

videos.description: Daniel Gafford grabs the missed layup and throws it back down for the big two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Gafford throws down putback dunk for Razorbacks

videos.description: Daniel Gafford puts the exclamation point on Arkansas' victory over Florida with a huge windmill dunk near the end of regulation.
videos.headline: Gafford slams massive windmill dunk
